snippet.title: Best VGM 815 - Star Fox - Fortuna
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 160 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TS8q1pjWviA

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Star Fox (1993)
Fortuna
Hajime Hirasawa
